  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Numerous studies have examined mathematics teachers' perceptions of the use of GeoGebra.",
    "Bu et al. (2013), Hutkemri and Nordin (2011), Doruk et al. (2013) and Zengin (2017b) investigated the perspectives of both in-service and pre-service mathematics teachers.",
    "Overall, these studies revealed generally positive perceptions of the application of GeoGebra in mathematics classrooms.",
    "Bu et al. (2013) identified several benefits of GeoGebra reported by mathematics teachers, including personal mathematical research, improved attitudes towards mathematics and mathematics education and enhanced pedagogical reflection.",
    "Hutkemri and Nordin (2011) observed that respondents expressed interest in using GeoGebra to explain mathematical concepts and procedures."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Bu et al. (2013), Hutkemri and Nordin (2011), Doruk et al. (2013) and Zengin (2017b) investigated the perspectives of both in-service and pre-service mathematics teachers.",
